<sections.6>
Human 2 is predicted to produce 15 different m. RNA transcripts, of which 7 would be protein coding (Ensembl) (Supplementary Fig. 3a). We designed cDNA primers to differentially amplify all protein encoding NBEAL2 transcripts (Supplementary Fig. 3) and tested RNA from a variety of human hematopoietic cells and other tissues. A unique combination of transcripts encoding NBEAL2-001, 201/003, 203/004 and 202 was expressed in megakaryocytes and platelets (Supplementary Table 1).
</sections.6>

